celltypes_loc <- "/project2/gilad/jpopp/ebQTL/data/single_cell_objects/highpass_cellid_all.pseudobulk-scran.tsv"

cell.types <- read_tsv(celltypes_loc, n_max=0, col_select=-c(1)) %>%
  colnames() %>%
  sapply(function(s){str_split(s, "_")[[1]][2]}) %>% 
  unique()
